    ka "就想让你尝试弹奏，但是，{p}对了……{p}左手借给我吧。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:691
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_f04ec3f3:

    # extend "Wait.{w=.3} What's wrong, not feeling well?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 488-493)
    extend "「啊、{w=.3}唔。」洸哉接过我的手，仔细地引导着"

# game/day 8.rpy:692
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_98c0eea5:

    # fn "「Whu... Oh! Sorry, I'm fine.{p} I was spacing out a little.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 494-496)
    fn "手指往正确的压弦位置。当手指绕过琴脖时，"

# game/day 8.rpy:696
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_4d1c25a4:

    # ka "「Your face is kind of red though.{p} You didn't catch a cold did you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 497-499)
    ka "能够感觉到琴弦那一丝硬的触感。不过比起那更重要的是，感觉到从洸哉手上传来的热量，"

# game/day 8.rpy:697
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_d43397e8:

    # fn "「That can't b-{w=.3} I'm fine, really.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 500-502)
    fn "心跳突然加速起来。啊……不知道为什么，这种暖暖的触感让我感觉到很幸福……"

# game/day 8.rpy:701
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_9dcc10df:

    # ka "「...Huh. If you say so, then all right.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 505-507)
    ka "「那么，首先这样就好了。{p}[fn]，现在――{p}喂，{w=.3}怎么了吗，没问题吧？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:702
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_c7ea5896:

    # fn "「Yeah,{w=.3} I'm totally okay.{p} Anyway, how do I play this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 509-511)
    fn "「诶！？{p}　……啊，{w=.3}抱歉没问题啦。{p}只是发了一下呆而已。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:703
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_7ea757a3:

    # "I changed the subject back to the guitar.\nWhatever's on Kouya's mind is a mystery,{p}but he seems not to be giving it too much thought."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 514-516)
    "「但是脸变得很红啊？{p}是感冒了吗」"

# game/day 8.rpy:704
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_7f8b328c:

    # "Man, that was close.{p}I don't really get what happened,{p}but it was close."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 518-523)
    "「怎么会，真的什么事都没有啦。」「……啊，既然你本人都那么说了应该没问题吧。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:710
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_ee113ecf:

    # ka "「For now, push down firmly with these fingers\n then play like you did before.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 525-527)
    ka "「唔唔，{w=.3}没关系没关系。{p}说起来这个要怎么弹才好呢？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:711
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_18138a05:

    # "I did as he asked, then tried it out."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 529)
    "把这个话题切断，想要返回原来的话题。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:712
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_ab01c5da:

    # "This time, the sound was different than before.{p}When I played with no strings,\nthe sound was very open and free..."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 530-531)
    "洸哉带着好奇的眼神看着我，不过因为我坚决的话也没有深究。"

# game/day 8.rpy:713
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_1e2d6a3e:

    # "But this time, the note cut off awkwardly."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 533)
    "呀，真危险啊。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:714
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_f65d4ee8:

    # "Even I could tell that I'd done something wrong."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 534)
    "虽然自己也不知道有什么危险的，"

# game/day 8.rpy:715
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_5974ff0a:

    # fn "「...I did something wrong,{w} huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 535-538)
    fn "总之很危险就是了。"

# game/day 8.rpy:719
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_7a293f25:

    # ka "「Yep. You did well in holding down the strings,{p} but holding the neighboring strings by accident\n could mess everything up.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 539-540)
    ka "「那么，用拇指以外的三根手指按在现在摸着的地方，{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:723
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_a53fd950:

    # ka "「Everyone sucks in the beginning, though.{p} I didn't get good all of a sudden, either.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 541-543)
    ka "然后用刚才那样的方式弹弹看。」像洸哉说的那样压住弦，试着弹了一下。"

# game/day 8.rpy:727
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_966db0cf:

    # ka "「Getting to being able to play that well\n is just a matter of practice.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 545-546)
    ka "因为振动数的变化音高也随之变化了。{p}不同于没有压住琴弦时声音的广阔与自由，"

# game/day 8.rpy:728
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_5b52a8a6:

    # fn "「Hmm, I guess instruments are really hard.{p} If I keep playing my fingers will hurt more{p} I can still see the marks on them.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 547-549)
    fn "这时尾音消失得十分不自然。就连我，也发现是有什么地方没有做好。"

# game/day 8.rpy:732
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_6ea750ef:

    # ka "「If you keep it up, it gets better.{p} It's always like that when you start.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 551-555)
    ka "「……失败了{p}吗？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:733
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_a6a26947:

    # fn "「Perseverance becomes strength, I guess...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 556-557)
    fn "「啊，压弦是没错了，不过不小心碰到了旁边的弦所以"

# game/day 8.rpy:734
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_e6c1ecb3:

    # ka "「Basically.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 558-562)
    ka "让声音变得奇怪了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:735
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_8b751519:

    # fn "「So, can I keep trying for a little longer?{p} Stopping just like that feels a little irritating.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 563-564)
    fn "「没关系啦，一开始大家都是这样的。{p}我也一样，也不能一下子就完美的弹奏整个曲子。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:739
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_2e5032a0:

    # ka "「Sure, I don't mind.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 567-569)
    ka "「所以想要熟练、漂亮地弹奏的话，练习就变得很必要了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:740
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_b9160613:

    # fn "「Thanks, Kouya. Let's see...{p} So I'm not supposed to touch the other strings?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 571-573)
    fn "「唔，乐器什么的果然还是很难啊。{p}而且总觉得，要是继续的话指尖就快要痛起来了。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:744
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_b998abb1:

    # ka "「Right, if you keep pressing\n your fingertips vertically...」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 574-577)
    ka "只是压了一次弦，就留下印痕了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:752
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_400bffc1:

    # "The sound rang out, loud and clear,{p}then slowly faded into the surrounding area."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 578-579)
    "「如果持续练习的话，那个也会变得不要紧的。{p}一开始的时候都是那样的。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:753
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_09080cd1:

    # "Kouya praised me, and applauded."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 581-582)
    "「坚持就是胜利，这样的意思吗？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:757
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_26b3d191:

    # ka "「Oho, you got better!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 584-587)
    ka "「就是这样。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:758
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_ce7f09b9:

    # fn "「All because of your help.{p} Really, thanks.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 588-589)
    fn "「唔唔。{p}这么说的话，可以再让我弹一会儿吗？{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:762
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_3bfaceb1:

    # ka "「Nah, it's not that.{p} You kept trying until the end.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 590-594)
    ka "停在这里总觉得很不甘心。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:766
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_bd53cc63:

    # ka "「Like, if you do it, then you will.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 595-597)
    ka "「啊，没关系的。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:767
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_63ff0a72:

    # fn "「Hahaha. Then I'll keep that in mind.{p} Anyway, all this holding down makes my fingers hurt.{p} My left hand is dead.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 598-599)
    fn "「谢谢，洸哉。{p}那个，不碰到旁边的弦就可以了吧。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:768
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_4907c80f:

    # "While I said that, I pulled up the guitar,\nfrom my lap and handed it back to Kouya."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 602-603)
    "「对对，用指尖垂直地压住琴弦――」"

# game/day 8.rpy:769
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_dc9aaca6:

    # "If I stay any longer I'd probably get in the way,\nso this might be a good point to go back."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 614)
    "做了好几次挑战，终于发出的声音"

# game/day 8.rpy:773
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_7ebaa8af:

    # ka "「Hm, good work there.{p} Did you have fun?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 615-617)
    ka "能够渐渐融入周围的空气后消失。洸哉听到了那个琴声，为我赞赏地鼓掌。"

# game/day 8.rpy:774
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_e31dfb72:

    # fn "「Yeah, it was great.{p} Thank you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 621-624)
    fn "「嗯，进行得很顺利呀。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:778
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_a2c7425d:

    # ka "「No need to thank me.{p} If you had fun, that's all that matters.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 625-626)
    ka "「嗯，多亏了洸哉认真仔细地教我的缘故。{p}真是{w=.3}谢谢了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:779
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_583203d2:

    # fn "「Are you going back to practice after this?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 629-631)
    fn "「不，没有那样的事。{p}是因为你一直到最后都很努力。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:783
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_c48c1300:

    # ka "「I was thinking of doing some more before going back.{p} What about you? Wanna listen for a little longer?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 634-637)
    ka "「有志者事竟成。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:784
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_cbad0601:

    # fn "「Nah, I've already gotten in the way,{p} so I'm about to head back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 638-639)
    fn "「啊哈哈，{w=.3}之前也说过那样的话呢。{p}不过说起来，一直压着弦果然手指很痛啊。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:788
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_c22300dc:

    # ka "「I see.{p} We have a live concert coming up,\n so you could come to that, if you want.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 640-642)
    ka "左手的HP已经归零了。」这么说着我从膝盖上拿起吉他，"

# game/day 8.rpy:789
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_bb63b8e6:

    # ka "「And not just the guitar,\n I want you to hear the whole band perform.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 643-645)
    ka "把它交还给洸哉。在这样下去就会妨碍到洸哉的练习了，"

# game/day 8.rpy:790
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_7299764b:

    # fn "「Oh,{w=.3} really?{p} That sounds like fun.{w} When is it?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 646-649)
    fn "今天就这样回去会比较好吗？"

# game/day 8.rpy:794
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_efcb1c7d:

    # ka "「Somewhere around the second half of the month.{p} I have a spare ticket, so if it's really okay,\n please come.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 650-651)
    ka "「哦，{w=.3}辛苦了。{p}好玩吗？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:795
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_201495e8:

    # fn "「Right, I'll be there for sure.{p} I'm looking forward to it, okay?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 653-655)
    fn "「嗯，很好玩呦。{p}真的很感谢你，{w=.3}洸哉。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:799
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_3f0c99c2:

    # ka "「Yeah, just watch me.{p} I'll give you the best performance ever.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 658-660)
    ka "「别那么拘礼啦。{p}如果能够开心，那再好不过了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:800
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_6945dee5:

    # fn "「I'll hold you to that.{p} Well, later then, Kouya.{p} Good luck with your practice!」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 662-666)
    fn "「洸哉在这之后还要练习吗？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:804
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_5ce0b3d6:

    # ka "「Right, take care as you go home.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 667-668)
    ka "「是的，我打算稍微练习一下再回去。[fn]要怎么版呢？　要再听一会儿吗？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:808
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_66dacb83:

    # "I waved, then went off on my own."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 670-671)
    "「不，打扰到你就不好了，我也差不多该回去了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:809
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_85c3857d:

    # "A live concert, huh?{p}I've never been to anything like that,{p}so it sounds really fun."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 674-678)
    "「这样啊。{p}我接下来有一个现场演奏会，如果你能来的话就好了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:810
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_b126a8ec:

    # "Since it's somewhere past mid-month,{p}I should keep things open."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 679-680)
    "「不仅仅是吉他，我想让你听一下乐团的演奏。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:814
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_9a92fddd:

    # "As I decided that, I walked back along the path,{p}moving with a lighter gait this time."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 682-684)
    "「啊，{w=.3}真的吗？{p}那还挺有趣的。{p}什么时候呢？」"

# game/day 8.rpy:815
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_teachme_a5d4be09:

    # "I didn't think that I'd like it all that much,{p}but walking through the forests is quite nice."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 687-689)
    "「中旬结束左右的时候。{p}这次刚好有多的票，如果能来的话就太好了。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:824
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_79c49943:

    # fn "「Hmm, I came all this way but I think I'll pass.{p} If I'm here, you can't take a break can you?」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 691-696)
    fn "「嗯，一定会去的。{p}真是十分期待啊。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:828
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_38a61f35:

    # ka "「No, it's not like that...{p} But I guess I should thank you\n for your consideration.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 697-698)
    ka "「啊，交给我吧。{p}一定会让你听到最棒的演奏会的。」"

# game/day 8.rpy:829
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_2c98a3e6:

    # fn "「Sorry, Kouya.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 700-702)
    fn "「那么就拜托你啦。{p}那么，下次见啦，{p}洸哉。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:833
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_07b025d8:

    # ka "「Nah, nothing you need to apologize for.{p} But if you ever do have time, get in touch with me,{p} and I'll teach you.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 703-706)
    ka "练习，{w=.3}要加油啊！」"

# game/day 8.rpy:834
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_14ef26e3:

    # fn "「Okay. Next time, for sure.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 707-711)
    fn "「啊，回去的时候要小心啊。」挥了挥手，和洸哉告别。"

# game/day 8.rpy:838
translate chinese_simplified kouya08_pass_e80895eb:

    # ka "「Take care on your way back.」"
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: 洸哉_s_03.ks (KS 713-714)
    ka "现场演奏啊。{p}因为完全没有去过，真的是很期待啊。{p}"

# game/day 8.rpy:839
